high_descs: turn right and move to the end of the room, then hang a left and move to the that end of the room, turn left and face the black table
pick up the cardboard box on the floor in front of the black table
turn left and move to the red couch on the right side of the room
place the cardboard box on the couch
turn around and walk nearly to the end of the room, then turn right and walk to the table near the end of the room, approach the right side of the table and face it
grab the keys off of the table there
turn left and find your way around all the objects in the room to get back to the couch on the left side of the room
place the keys in the box on the right side of the couch and close the box
anns.task_desc: place a box with keys in it on the right side of the red couch

high_descs: Turn to your right and walk forward, then hang a left when you reach the wall, then turn left and walk to the box next to the nightstand.
Pick up the box next to the nightstand.
Walk to the red couch across from you.
Place the box on the right side of the couch, to the right of the remote.
Turn around and walk toward the fireplace, then hang a right and walk to the glass dining table.
Pick up the set of keys off the table that are furthest from the laptop.
Turn left and walk back toward the red couch next to the TV.
Place the keys inside the box on the couch and then close the box.
anns.task_desc: Place a closed box with a set of keys inside on the red couch.

high_descs: Begin waking forward, then turn right and walk across the room, then hang a left and walk over to where the cardboard box is resting on the ground.
Pick up the cardboard box off of the ground.
Turn left and walk over to the couch with two remotes and a credit card on it.
Place the cardboard box on the rightmost couch seat cushion to the right of the remote.
Turn left and take a step, then turn left again and walk over to the glass table with the laptop on it.
Pick up the keys off of the glass table.
Turn left and walk back over to where the cardboard box is resting on the couch.
Put the keys in the cardboard box and close the box.
anns.task_desc: Close a cardboard box with keys inside.
